1.title: Gestrandet
1.plot: Gestrandet) Two North Sea fishermen find he corpse of 21-year old Sofie Albers, had smashed, baby son Leon on arm. Her mother Rika suspects troublesome loser Sophie's stepfather Holger. Lars Englen and Finn Kiesewetter's Lübeck police team soon realize the boat isn't the murder site. Suspects include baby Leon's father ex-junkie father Peter Jansen, who was turned down despite finally finding a mechanic job, Sophie's mystery diary lover and her last caller, married ex-lover MD Knud Lorenz whose greedy wife covers for him. New crimes and a maternal instinct gone wild ...
